                <h2>6. Reflection: What? So What? What Next?</h2>
                <h3>What?</h3>
                <p>This project will allow me to bring together my AI learning and professional infrastructure experience into one focused piece of work.</p>
                <h3>So What?</h3>
                <p>The project is important because it will demonstrate my ability to move from academic learning to practical implementation and critical evaluation.</p>
                <h3>What Next?</h3>
                <p>I plan to identify a project topic that connects Artificial Intelligence with networking, predictive automation, intelligent monitoring, or real-world decision support.</p>

